{"tid":1825750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"電槍好危險㗎","createTime":"2020-01-15T14:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:32:12.000Z","uid":323588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6fce007fd5c722c6879179e890bb7a01430a1364","tid":1825750,"uid":323588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"去旅行嘅大家入嚟睇下，到時有人用電槍射你都知點做，出面治安可以好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.com.au/technology/taser-tactics-police-share-their-shocking-secrets/news-story/a208ae6bf5f923fe287f9bb6b52cc922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Ftechnology%2Ftaser-tactics-police-share-their-shocking-secrets%2Fnews-story%2Fa208ae6bf5f923fe287f9bb6b52cc922&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=4fee6b3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.com.au/technology/taser-tactics-police-share-their-shocking-secrets/news-story/a208ae6bf5f923fe287f9bb6b52cc922</a>"},{"pid":"c4a95fac277247f6f988b9fcb3e3948d76c63fd8","tid":1825750,"uid":323588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"重點：<br />\n1. 盡量喺射手嘅視角向左或右走，避免被人射中<br />\n2. 電槍射程一般唔過十米，因為有兩條電線<br />\n3. 盡量減低兩個 contact 嘅距離，寧願局部痛楚都要避免被電流擊倒<br />\n4. 面對射手，被人射中可以用手嘗試掃走兩個或其中一個 contact"},{"pid":"e0ccc40dd028437f3e95a2580b0516bdcfcc7c4a","tid":1825750,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoF3XaL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoF3XaL.png&h=9bd36e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mWD2RbKXX8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmWD2RbKXX8I&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=731ec06a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mWD2RbKXX8I</a><br />\ncls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果